  "slug": "kleeslabs",
  "title": "KleeSlabs",
  "description": "Break only the half of a double slab that you're looking at.",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://blay09.net/files/brand/kleeslabs.png\" alt=\"KleeSlabs\" width=\"836\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<p style=\"display: flex;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/balm\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://mods.twelveiterations.com/img/requires-balm.png\" alt=\"Requires Balm\" width=\"260\" height=\"80\"></a> <a href=\"https://mods.twelveiterations.com/sponsor\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img style=\"margin-left: 26px;\" src=\"https://mods.twelveiterations.com/img/new-patreon.png\" alt=\"Support on Patreon\" width=\"550\" height=\"80\"></a></p>\n<p>This mod allows you to break only one half of a double slab. The half that is broken depends on which half you're looking at.</p>\n<p>It supports Vanilla slabs as well as many modded slabs. Modded slabs that do not work yet should be reported on the Issue Tracker.</p>\n<p>This mod is available for NeoForge, Fabric and Forge. It requires <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/balm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Balm</a>, which must be installed alongside the mod.</p>\n<h3><img src=\"https://mods.twelveiterations.com/img/features-header.png\" alt=\"Features\" width=\"836\" height=\"40\"></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Break only the half of a double slab that you're looking at</li>\n<li>Supports all Vanilla slabs</li>\n<li>Supports slabs from many different mods</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/63/864/kleeslabs194.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"847\" height=\"464\"></p>\n<h3><img src=\"https://mods.twelveiterations.com/img/credits-header.png\" alt=\"Features\" width=\"836\" height=\"40\"></h3>\n<p>This mod was made by suggestion of <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/kleetho\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kleetho</a> during one of her Subathons, hence the name.</p>",
